Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:43.89,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(498,0)}Can't focus. My body is still puzzled about what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.65,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I'm trembling. I can't stop even if I try to control myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:51.40,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Although neither sun nor moon are on my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:52.82,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}"I've no choice but to try,"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:55.49,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Those were the words I muttered to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:01.08,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(298,0)}The odds aren't on my side, but running way'd be gutless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:05.08,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(298,0)}Even if I can't see the future, I'll just have to win it over with courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:08.58,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Need to keep distance from the target as I hold myself back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:11.88,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(298,0)}All that's needed for victory is pride to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:14.97,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Will we celebrate with the wine of victory
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:18.97,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Or'll we end up kissing their feet in defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:22.72,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}There are two outcomes to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:26.44,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}I want to control destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:31.77,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I need to seize the golden opportunity with my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:35.86,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I'll finish it up with my best poker face,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:40.78,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,458)}And drag them into a world of illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:47.16,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I'll find my way out of this endless pressure game,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:51.17,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}And leap over the borderline of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:55.88,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}How many? What'll I need to sacrifice to make it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:02:00.14,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,500)}What is the one thing I don't want to let go?
