Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.52,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to let loose like this every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:22.03,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You probably think we're the most carefree people on earth, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:27.79,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,But who can blame us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:33.46,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,This country's always at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:43.55,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,And now there's something going on over in Ishval... is that all this country is good for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:49.85,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,They never learn. {ep 05}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:52.81,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are foolish, pitiful creatures. {ep 05; edited}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:19.92,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,With Ishbal and other riots...\Nthe East sure have their hands full. {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:24.64,Default,Fok,0000,0000,0000,,Not just the East, but there are riots and border wars\Nsparking up in the North and the West. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:31.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Skirmishes are still ongoing on the border with Aerugo to the south and Creta to the west. {ep15}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And there's still the great nation of Drachma up north, too. {ep 15}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:38.32,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Mountains of corpses everywhere, huh... {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.90,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,We may even get a coup soon... {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.41,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Such a scary country to be in... {ep 15}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:49.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This country's been so military-focused ever since King Bradley became the Führer President. {ep 15}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.34,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:02.59,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite the stud, Hohenheim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:06.30,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go dance by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.35,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,But that's no fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:12.77,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,This man isn't fancy enough to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:16.48,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, go dance with those girls over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.57,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's about how old they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:29.91,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,...when they started to even think about something like human transmutation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:42.88,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you take a stand as\Ntheir father and say something to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:51.52,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did, it wouldn't change the fact they'd have to repent for their sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.73,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You're harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:56.85,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,A sin is a sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!!! {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They took it away!!! {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Help me... someone... {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mom... Mom... {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No way... No...  {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:26.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't... {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what I wanted!!! {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al... Alphonse... {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse! Alphonse! {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Because of me... {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse!!! {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:45.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit... Dammit!!! {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Give him back... He's my little brother... {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it be an arm or a leg... {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Or even my heart! You can take it! {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So give him back... {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He's my only brother!!! {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:11.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A heavenly stone that destroyed Xerxes overnight. {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:16.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If we had this, we could get your body back... {ep 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:22.23,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, what exactly were you ordered to research? {ep 06}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:24.98,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,The Philosopher's Stone. {ep 06}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.53,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't desire such a thing. {ep 06}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.61,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Devil's research. {ep 06}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.57,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see Hell if you study it. {ep 06}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"The Devil's research"... {ep 07}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:38.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"Something you mustn't desire"... {ep 07}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I resent you, Dr. Marcoh... {ep 07}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The ingredients of philosopher's stones... {ep 07}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...are live humans. {ep 07}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Fragile beings, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:20.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They cower at the darkness and don't try to stand up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:24.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And instead, they try to forget it temporarily and try to escape from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:28.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are such weak creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:37.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's have them be of some use\Nto us as a precious resource.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Hohenheim?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:56.99,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,"You may be able to reach\Nthe real truth that is beyond truth"... {ep 07}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this? {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:05.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be what's used to transmute philosopher's stones? {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:10.42,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how good you are. {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.76,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like that arm saved your life! {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:20.14,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,But my beloved sword even slices through steel! {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:47.42,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.92,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,It's shameful, but we lost. {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:54.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to say something like, "Hey, we're actually a trio", are ya? {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.26,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,We won't, we won't. {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:59.60,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Just destroy us already, boy. {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Spare me from having to murder someone. {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.35,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,You consider us human? {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:14.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't accept you two as human,\Nit would mean I'm doing the same to my brother, too. {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:19.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,My little brother is human. {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And so are you two. {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:24.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I don't want to kill you. {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.50,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Brother? {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:36.05,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Us two have been stealing, destroying,\Nand murdering ever since we came of age. {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:41.47,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,And we're being treated as humans for the first time, after being turned into this? {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.14,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.  {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:47.44,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you everything as a parting gift, boy. {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:52.73,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,The one who created the philosopher's stone and told us to guard this place is... {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.99,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,That was close. {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:02.70,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be saying out things like that, 48. {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.83,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying, dumbass! {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:12.63,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were about to kill a precious sacrifice! {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.84,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand?! {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:17.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you two?! {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:19.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What plan?! {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by sacrifice?! {ep 08}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:25.06,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,You're a human sacrifice, right? {ep 25}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:29.06,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, that's right. I'm a human sacrifice! {ep 25}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:32.15,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck does he mean by that? {ep 25}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:36.57,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,...and perhaps their master, too... may also be a suitable sacrifice {ep 14; paraphrased}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:39.53,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:42.49,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,You're a candidate for sacrifice, {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:44.08,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,but you're going to die here. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.95,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking for some time.. {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:51.50,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,...as to what you mean by "human sacrifice"... {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:56.88,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,...and about what you are trying to make me do.. {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:01.18,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Riots throughout Lior. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.68,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,The ingredients of philosopher's stone are humans... {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:08.06,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,What we did in Ishval... {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:14.06,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa now, who's the mastermind behind all of this? {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:17.15,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,What you are trying to do right now... {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:21.78,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,...is to create a giant transmutation circle, using this country and its people. {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.16,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,And the purpose of that... {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:27.70,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,...is to create a philosopher's stone. Am I right? {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:42.43,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you actually knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.43,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Hohenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.89,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.68,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Hohenheim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:57.48,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I had, would that have changed anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:58.57,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.49,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I've been watching them for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:11.25,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,The humans who continue to repeat the same mistakes without end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:18.09,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,And the same humans who had to helplessly escape from their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:26.89,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are fragile creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.64,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:33.35,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,The philosopher's stone is my core. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.35,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a homunculus. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:37.69,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of them, have you? {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:40.11,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Humans that were created artificially. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:43.32,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I am. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:48.12,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,We're all going to die here anyway. {ep 25}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:51.49,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you something cool as a final gift. {ep 25}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.09,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Can I eat him? {ep 05 or 07}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.01,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang!!! {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:15.89,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,The monster was keeping another monster inside its belly! {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.86,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,It swallowed everything around him! {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So even something like this is created... {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...by alchemy... {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.36,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, old man? {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:40.13,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you have an ultimate shield, {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:42.96,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I have an ultimate eye. {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.52,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now I get it, Hughes... {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.40,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,When you said that the army was in danger... {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:05.90,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...you didn't mean a crisis was approaching the army... {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:09.32,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You meant that the army itself was in a crisis. {ep 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:16.08,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Father? You have a dad? {ep 25}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:17.91,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I do. {ep 25}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The one who created the Homunculi? {ep 25}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.63,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {ep 25}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:32.39,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Humans don't have an ultimate spear or an ultimate shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:40.56,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, the most trivial things get the best of them, making them unable to get back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:49.61,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What can creatures like that do against homunculi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:52.49,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, we won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.41,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't give up for the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:07.42,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That's also a human trait, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:10.51,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,How can you even move with that wound?! {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.30,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I sealed it with fire! {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.51,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Although I almost fainted a few times. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:22.77,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times you try, you can't win. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:28.57,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,How about you tell me the secret now? {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for that. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:38.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The blood that was all up in my head went away, and I can think clearly now. {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.75,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going to resist? {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:48.09,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Let this put you to sleep! {ep 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:59.52,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,This body comes with many inconveniences. {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:02.69,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But inconveniences don't make me miserable! {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:04.98,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for you to pity me! {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:09.28,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,My life was put together with alchemy by my brother. {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:15.24,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,If I deny myself, that would mean that I'm denying brother, along with alchemy. {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:19.41,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in the potential that alchemy holds. {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:20.54,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe in it! {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.12,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,A State Alchemist! {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.01,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Get down! {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.68,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there... {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.02,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die! {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:50.32,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit... It won't stop bleeding... {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.19,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:04.66,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Live... {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:06.54,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,You can't die. {ep 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:09.96,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Lan Fan! {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:10.80,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Run! {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:13.84,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Lan Fan!!! {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.59,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,My left arm is... {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.14,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.68,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master! {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:22.18,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer be of any use to you! {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:24.85,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Lan Fan?! {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.19,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it! {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.69,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Well played. {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:38.70,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times we're stepped on...\NNo matter how many times we fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.45,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get back up and keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.54,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,And someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.50,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a useless struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.00,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know until you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:51.75,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than not doing anything at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.09,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you fine with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:59.05,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,If Ed, Al, and everyone else disappears?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:07.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting so worked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:13.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we do work for the sake of the humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:17.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,they'll just end up dying in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It all becomes wasted effort on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:29.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, don't you think it's wiser to simply grab what's important and run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:30.42,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What did y-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:35.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A bit of your conscience?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Or a worthless sentiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Hohenheim?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:47.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard you try,\Nno one will accept you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at your own face!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:01.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are nothing but a resource to be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:04.37,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And if you leave them be, they'll renew themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:08.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you need to do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:11.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Would that change anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be able to change reality?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:17.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be able to change how these weak humans are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.35,Default,Trisha,0000,0000,0000,,We can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.52,Default,Trisha,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.02,Default,Trisha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.74,Default,Trisha,0000,0000,0000,,We really are weak creatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:45.83,Default,Trisha,0000,0000,0000,,but that's why we can strive to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:49.37,Default,Trisha,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you feel it's useless,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:54.00,Default,Trisha,0000,0000,0000,,each step we take leads to something great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,A subordinate protects their subordinate, and so forth. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.43,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That should be possible, even for us puny humans. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:06.26,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,No... I wasn't prepared enough. {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:11.56,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Lan Fan was more prepared than I was. {ep 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:13.94,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing people die before my eyes... {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:16.11,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it! I'm tired of it! {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:19.78,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to let anyone die anymore! I'll protect you! {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No way in hell am I going to run! {ep 20}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:28.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,After I beat the shit out of that "truth" guy, I'm going to drag your body out of there! {ep 20}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:29.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al! {ep 26}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:32.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al! Come here! {ep 26}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:35.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Al!!! {ep 26}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:40.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse! {ep 26}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse! {ep 26}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse! {ep 26}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me. {ep 26}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.60,Default,Trisha,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm sure we'll be able to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:55.27,Default,Trisha,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're weak... and because death is inevitable...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:59.61,Default,Trisha,0000,0000,0000,,Humans try their best to live and end up becoming stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:04.11,Default,Trisha,0000,0000,0000,,If your heart is still hesitating...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.03,Default,Trisha,0000,0000,0000,,Try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:12.25,Default,Trisha,0000,0000,0000,,The days you spent in Resembool with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.46,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,A dream, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:22.65,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:03.58,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll cower at the sight of the great foe before you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.58,0:24:06.17,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,leave at once, coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.79,0:24:09.38,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll lose the strength you believed in,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.38,0:24:12.01,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,then fall to the ground, weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.63,0:24:14.47,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time for the decisive battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.47,0:24:16.85,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Humans, give it all you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.85,0:24:22.48,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:25.65,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 28, Father.
